title: Kate Spade: Up to 75% Off Surprise Sale = $32 Wallets, $79 Handbags & More
text:
Calling all you fans of Kate Spade! Through today only, head on over to KateSpade.com and enter your email address and zip code to access the Surprise Sale to score 75% off select items.

I spotted iPhone cases for $19 (regularly $45), necklaces and earrings from $19 (regularly $78), wallets from $32 (regularly $128), shopper totes from $59 (regularly $148), handbags from $79 (regularly $229) and more. Shipping is a flat rate of $5 or free on $175+ orders.
